e… ausdrücken kann", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Neokortex unser “Aussichtspunkt”", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Neuropsychologie des Traumas", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Notfallnummern:", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "PHASEN DER MIGRATION", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "POTENTIELL TRAUMATISCHE EREIGNISSE", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "PRAXISBEISPIELE FÜR KULTURSENSIBLE KOMMUNIKATION", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "PSYCHOSOZIALE FOLGEN VON IDENTITÄTSVERLUST", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Paradoxie der traumatischen Situation", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Phasen der Stabilisierung", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Phasen des Migrationsprozesses", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Phasenorientierte Therapie", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Primat der Begegnung", "target": "attitude", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "attitude"}, {"source": "Prävalenzen:Folgen der Gewalt", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Prävention", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Prävention & Resilienzförderung", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Psychische Folgen", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Psychodynamik der Traumatisierung & das Verlaufsmodell nach Fischer", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Psychoedukation", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Psychohygiene", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Psychologische Erste Hilfe für Geflüchtete\nhttps://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1V_5iL_pZTNjkazJ3p7-zAzlm44h6FuZ8/edit?slide=id.p12#slide=id.p12", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Pädagogik der Selbstbemächtigung (Weiß, 2009)", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Quellen:", "target": "attitude", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "attitude"}, {"source": "Resilienz fördern – innere Stärke entwickeln", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Ressourcen", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Ressourcenanker", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "SPRACHBARRIEREN & KULTURELLE TABUSSPRACHBARRIEREN – MEHR ALS FEHLENDE WORTE", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "STABILISIERUNG - WAS IST DAS?", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Sandor Ferenczi: Identifikation mit dem Aggressor", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Schutzkonzepte & psychosoziale Unterstützung", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Schwierigkeiten", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Schützende Faktoren", "target": "attitude", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "attitude"}, {"source": "Sicherheit", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Soziale & kollektive Traumaweitergabe", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Spezifische Hintergründe der Flucht von Mädchen und Frauen", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Spezifische Übertragungsangebote in der sozialen Arbeit", "target": "attitude", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "attitude"}, {"source": "Spüre einmal die Weichheit eines Kleidungsstücks ganz bewusst für einige Momente auf der Haut, streiche mit der Hand über einen für Dich angenehmen Stoff und spür einen Moment lang diesem Empfinden in den Fingerspitzen etwas nach.", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Stabilisierung kann nur auf freiwilliger Basis geschehen.", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Stabilisierungstechniken", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Starre (Freeze)", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Stress reduzieren", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Struktureller & individueller Rassismus", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Symptome", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "TRAUMA UND MIGRATION & KULTURSENSIBLE ARBEIT", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "TRAUMASCHEMA UND TRAUMAKOMPENSATORISCHES SCHEMA", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "TRAUMATISIERUNGEN KÖNNEN DAS LEBEN TIEFGREIFEND VERÄNDERN – BESONDERS, WENN SIE WIEDERHOLT UND IN BEZIEHUNGSKONTEXTEN STATTFINDEN.KOMPLEXE TRAUMATA BETREFFEN NICHT NUR DIE PSYCHE, SONDERN AUCH IDENTITÄT, BINDUNGSFÄHIGKEIT UND KÖRPERWAHRNEHMUNG.DIESE PRÄSENTATION GIBT EINEN ÜBERBLICK ÜBER URSACHEN, FOLGEN UND BEWÄHRTE INTERVENTIONSANSÄTZE BEI KOMPLEXER TRAUMATISIERUNG.", "target": "skill", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "skill"}, {"source": "Terminologisch korrekt könnte von einem \"psychotraumatischen Belastungssyndrom \" (PTBS) gesprochen werden (vgl. Fischer & Riedesser 1998), das durch ein traumatisches Erlebnis entsteht und sich Zeitraum nach dem Ereignis zu einem Störungsbild verfestigen kann. Man erlebt so, als ob man dem Ereignis immer noch ausgesetzt wäre, obwohl es bereits vorbei ist.", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Therapieansätze:", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Transgenerationale Weitergabe von Traumata", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Transgenerationale Weitergabe von Traumata (R. Barwinski)", "target": "attitude", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "attitude"}, {"source": "Transkulturalität", "target": "attitude", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "attitude"}, {"source": "Trauma", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Trauma & Flucht", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Trauma ist eine NORMALE psycho-physiologische Reaktion auf ein extrem bedrohliches, überlastendes Ereignis!", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Trauma- & schamsensible Gesprächsführung", "target": "attitude", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "attitude"}, {"source": "Traumafolgen", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Traumareaktive Entwicklungen", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Traumaschema (TS)", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Traumatisierte Kinder & Familien begleiten", "target": "knowledge", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "knowledge"}, {"source": "Traumatogene Psychodynamik traumatischer Gewalt", "target": "attitude", "type": "HAS_COMPETENCE", "value": "attitude"}, {"source": "Typen der Traumatisierung (